Finance/Currency/Convert/Yahoo version 0.01
===========================================

Using Finance.Yahoo.com, converts a sum between two currencies.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	strict;
	warnings;
	LWP::UserAgent;
	HTTP::Request;
	HTML::TokeParser;

